HEADWORD: cross-index
<hw>cross-index</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a reference at one place in a
work to information at another place in the same work.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cross-reference.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

